    {"id": "p01", "author_id": "b01", "text": "My local store is running low on essentials again.", "timestamp": "2026-06-20T09:00:00Z"},
    {"id": "p02", "author_id": "b17", "text": "I checked three stores and supplies were inconsistent today.", "timestamp": "2026-06-20T09:03:00Z"},
    {"id": "p03", "author_id": "b02", "text": "People keep saying the shortage is worse than the store admits.", "timestamp": "2026-06-20T09:04:00Z"},
    {"id": "p04", "author_id": "b11", "text": "urgent stock warning share now", "timestamp": "2026-06-20T09:05:00Z"},
    {"id": "p05", "author_id": "b03", "text": "Wait times keep increasing and nobody is explaining why.", "timestamp": "2026-06-20T09:06:00Z"},
    {"id": "p06", "author_id": "b12", "text": "Store staff are saying shipments are delayed again.", "timestamp": "2026-06-20T09:07:00Z"},
    {"id": "p07", "author_id": "b04", "text": "I saw a thread saying shelves were being emptied on purpose.", "timestamp": "2026-06-20T09:08:00Z"},
    {"id": "p08", "author_id": "b13", "text": "The shortage rumor is spreading fast in local groups.", "timestamp": "2026-06-20T09:09:00Z"},
    {"id": "p09", "author_id": "b05", "text": "Could be panic buying, but the timing is weird.", "timestamp": "2026-06-20T09:10:00Z"},
    {"id": "p10", "author_id": "b14", "text": "share this before shelves are empty everywhere", "timestamp": "2026-06-20T09:11:00Z"},
    {"id": "p11", "author_id": "b06", "text": "I am not sure if this is real or just online exaggeration.", "timestamp": "2026-06-20T09:12:00Z"},
    {"id": "p12", "author_id": "b15", "text": "The same message keeps getting pushed all morning.", "timestamp": "2026-06-20T09:13:00Z"},
    {"id": "p13", "author_id": "b07", "text": "My cousin said the warehouse is struggling, but I have no proof.", "timestamp": "2026-06-20T09:14:00Z"},
    {"id": "p14", "author_id": "b16", "text": "People are starting to panic and buy extra because of the rumor.", "timestamp": "2026-06-20T09:15:00Z"},
    {"id": "p15", "author_id": "b08", "text": "The wait times at checkouts were up again this afternoon.", "timestamp": "2026-06-20T09:16:00Z"},
    {"id": "p16", "author_id": "b09", "text": "I think the store is short staffed, which makes it look worse.", "timestamp": "2026-06-20T09:17:00Z"},
    {"id": "p17", "author_id": "b10", "text": "There is a lot of chatter but not much verified evidence yet.", "timestamp": "2026-06-20T09:18:00Z"},
    {"id": "p18", "author_id": "b18", "text": "I saw one account telling everyone to share the shortage warning.", "timestamp": "2026-06-20T09:19:00Z"},
    {"id": "p19", "author_id": "b19", "text": "The rumor seems amplified by a few suspicious profiles.", "timestamp": "2026-06-20T09:20:00Z"},
